And we show you,
engine number seven,

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:06.087 align:middle line:84%
I call it laser accurate
priority planning.

00:09:06.087 --> 00:09:08.670 align:middle line:84%
>> We're so much more inclined
to do the easy stuff first even

00:09:08.670 --> 00:09:10.230 align:middle line:84%
though they may be
a C on the list.

00:09:10.230 --> 00:09:11.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:09:11.030 --> 00:09:12.980 align:middle line:84%
>> Get it out of the way so you
don't have to think about it.

00:09:12.980 --> 00:09:13.780 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:09:13.780 --> 00:09:15.950 align:middle line:84%
And because it is easy and
it's not uncomfortable,

00:09:15.950 --> 00:09:20.030 align:middle line:84%
but, oftentimes, the
most important things,

00:09:20.030 --> 00:09:21.310 align:middle line:90%
they are uncomfortable.

00:09:21.310 --> 00:09:22.880 align:middle line:90%
They take a little effort.

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:24.350 align:middle line:90%
They might be a little scary.

00:09:24.350 --> 00:09:26.890 align:middle line:84%
So those are the things
we tend to procrastinate.

00:09:26.890 --> 00:09:29.780 align:middle line:84%
>> And also, they need
a big slog of time.

00:09:29.780 --> 00:09:30.580 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:09:30.580 --> 00:09:31.538 align:middle line:90%
Well, we think they do.

00:09:31.538 --> 00:09:33.770 align:middle line:84%
Actually, when you start
to do it the right way,

00:09:33.770 --> 00:09:37.190 align:middle line:84%
you find out almost nothing
needs a lot of time.

00:09:37.190 --> 00:09:39.640 align:middle line:84%
It just needs focused
time where you're really

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:41.410 align:middle line:90%
focused on getting it done.

00:09:41.410 --> 00:09:44.170 align:middle line:84%
And this chapter alone
really puts a person

00:09:44.170 --> 00:09:47.470 align:middle line:84%
in charge of their day and puts
them into control of their day.

00:09:47.470 --> 00:09:48.980 align:middle line:90%
And it really is fulfilling.

00:09:48.980 --> 00:09:51.760 align:middle line:84%
It's liberating once you get
into the habit of doing it.

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:54.205 align:middle line:10%
>> Suppose you don't
know what your vision is,

00:09:54.205 --> 00:09:56.790 align:middle line:10%
do you still write down, "I
don't know what my vision is?"

00:09:56.790 --> 00:09:57.590 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:09:57.590 --> 00:09:59.980 align:middle line:84%
No, what you do is you
start out by dividing

00:09:59.980 --> 00:10:02.000 align:middle line:84%
your life into the most
important areas of life.

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:02.800 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:10:02.800 --> 00:10:04.810 align:middle line:84%
So some people have
three important areas,

00:10:04.810 --> 00:10:06.520 align:middle line:90%
some people have five.

00:10:06.520 --> 00:10:08.680 align:middle line:90%
I have seven important areas.

00:10:08.680 --> 00:10:11.430 align:middle line:84%
You then start in the
most important area.

00:10:11.430 --> 00:10:14.050 align:middle line:10%
And you say, OK, if I
could have anything I want,

00:10:14.050 --> 00:10:16.360 align:middle line:10%
anything, what would that be?

00:10:16.360 --> 00:10:18.577 align:middle line:84%
That becomes your
impossible dream, see.

00:10:18.577 --> 00:10:20.410 align:middle line:84%
And then we build the
road map to get there.

00:10:20.410 --> 00:10:20.690 align:middle line:90%
>> That's your vision.

00:10:20.690 --> 00:10:21.860 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:10:21.860 --> 00:10:23.110 align:middle line:90%
It's not as hard as you think.

00:10:23.110 --> 00:10:24.280 align:middle line:90%
>> Really.

00:10:24.280 --> 00:10:26.440 align:middle line:90%
So that's the key.

00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:29.147 align:middle line:84%
If I could have anything
I wanted in this area--

00:10:29.147 --> 00:10:29.980 align:middle line:90%
>> What would it be?

00:10:29.980 --> 00:10:30.970 align:middle line:90%
>> What would it be?

00:10:30.970 --> 00:10:33.440 align:middle line:90%
>> That's where you start.

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:38.620 align:middle line:84%
>> Wow, well that's quite
a way to start, I'll say.

00:10:38.620 --> 00:10:40.710 align:middle line:84%
We're talking to
Steven Scott here

00:10:40.710 --> 00:10:43.830 align:middle line:84%
who has written a book that
you don't want to miss.

00:10:43.830 --> 00:10:46.650 align:middle line:10%
It's called "Simple Steps
to Impossible Dreams--

00:10:46.650 --> 00:10:50.260 align:middle line:10%
The 15 Power Secrets
of the World's Most

00:10:50.260 --> 00:10:51.730 align:middle line:10%
Successful People."

00:10:51.730 --> 00:10:54.010 align:middle line:84%
And one of them is
sitting here with us.

00:10:54.010 --> 00:10:55.030 align:middle line:90%
So stay with us.

00:10:55.030 --> 00:10:56.830 align:middle line:84%
We have a lot more
interesting stuff

00:10:56.830 --> 00:11:00.202 align:middle line:90%
to ask this wonderful author.

